               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images 3r-133l: Funeral Ritual, መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት፡. Published more than once: መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት።  (Roma, 1908); መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት። ጸሎት፡ ላዕለ፡ ምውታን፡ (Addis Ababa: Tǝnśa’e Zä-Guba’e, 1944 E.C.); መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት። ጸሎት፡ ላዕለ፡ ምውታን፡ (Addis Ababa: Täsfa, 1962 E.C.). For the sources and detailed description, see the description of manuscript OR. 9645 SBPrK. Illuminations are added recently over text.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
